608
00:40:01,314 --> 00:40:02,614
Hola, Miranda.

609
00:40:05,214 --> 00:40:06,414
Por supuesto.

610
00:40:08,214 --> 00:40:09,914
Ajá.
Ahora mismo voy.

611
00:40:10,715 --> 00:40:11,715
Oh, Dios.

612
00:40:11,814 --> 00:40:14,514
